    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great, you\u2019ve gotta come check this one out!",
