    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The engine benefits from a dual-row ceramic IMS retrofit and a recent rear main seal replacement, ensuring mechanical longevity. Performance is sharp thanks to a factory-spec suspension refresh and a recent four-wheel alignment. The VarioCam Plus system provides a broad torque curve, while the chassis remains communicative and balanced. A mechanically robust example with a clean undercarriage and no signs of bore scoring, showing only minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age.",
      "price": 34500.0,
