    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle offers a fantastic blend of performance and comfort for the discerning driver. The exterior paint still holds a brilliant luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the trunk handle\u2014typical signs of a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is supple with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every feature, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the intuitive infotainment system, is in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service history that shows regular oil changes and a recent transmission flush. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car that delivers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
